import React from 'react'

const Dome = (props: any) => {
  return (
    <defs>
      <clipPath clipPathUnits="objectBoundingBox" id={props.type}>
      <rect
        id="rect10"
        width="93.171127"
        height="67.46875"
        x="-5.8760703e-09"
        y="227.26335"
        style="stroke-width:0.25989369"
        ry="33.734375"
        rx="46.113094" />
      <rect
        id="rect18"
        width="93.360107"
        height="34.017857"
        x="1.1564146e-06"
        y="263.17108"
        rx="0"
        ry="0"
        style="stroke-width:0.29918846" />
      </clipPath>
    </defs>
  )
}

export default Dome;
